# .conductor/ is worker scratch (resume notes, worktrees, logs) — ignore it,
# but ALWAYS keep the committed secrets manifest. Note: exclude the dir's
# *contents* (.conductor/*), never the dir itself, or the negation can't win.
.conductor/*
!.conductor/secrets.yaml
# <<< conductor-baseline
